 Fillings vary from region to region but one of the most popular is a rich meat ragù with peas. Arancini that are formed with mozzarella in the centre are called <i>arancini di riso al telefono<\/i> due to the mozzarella forming a long string like a telephone line when broken apart.","Add <b>1 cm<b> cubes of mozzarella in the middle of the arancini for extra flavour."],"basicInfo":["medium","45m","2h 10m","14 pieces"]}